\c 35 Josia anoitira Jehovha Pasika 1 Zvino Josia akaitira Jehovha Pasika paJerusaremu; vakauraya gwayana rePasika nezuva regumi namana romwedzi wokutanga. 2 Akagadza vapristi pamabasa avo, akavatsungisa pabasa reimba yaJehovha. 3 Akati kuna vaRevhi vaidzidzisa vaIsiraeri vose, vakanga vari vatsvene kuna Jehovha, "Isai areka tsvene muimba yakavakwa naSoromoni mwanakomana waDhavhidhi mambo walsiraeri; hamuchazovi nomutoro pamafudzi enyu; zvino, shumirai Jehovha Mwari wenyu, navanhu vake Isiraeri. 4 Zvigadzirei, nedzimba dzamadzibaba enyu namapoka
